Package: unity-gtk-module-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: unity-gtk-module0 (= ${binary:Version}), libgtk-3-dev (>= 3.2.0)
Description: GTK+ module for exporting old-style menus as GMenuModels
 Many applications implement menus as GtkMenuShells and GtkMenuItems
 and aren't looking to migrate to the newer GMenuModel API.
 .
 This GTK+ module watches for these types of menus and exports the
 appropriate GMenuModel implementation.
 .
 This package contains headers and documentation.

